data.description: Come check out this gem in Country Estates. Original hardwood floors and open concept for living area that gives a warmth throughout the home. All 3 bedrooms have new carpet and enjoy a built in sunroom/flex room.  The home offers a big backyard and spacious storage units. Covered patio and a single car garage and extended carport for extra vehicle converge. Book your showing today.
